This folder contains two folders, v2 and v3 which contain core controller code
The v2 folder is now an archive as the last version compatible with the old v2 ESP32 sdk
The v3 folder will contain code compatible with the v3 ESP32 SDK until a newer version exists

Development of the core controller is now running down with an empahsis on the dedicated controller
boards based on Arduino, Raspberry Pi and Pico which use the core controller board for control input, 
web serving and basic image processing
